    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Ready for your next road trip? This fantastic vehicle is in great shape and offers a smooth, reliable driving experience that you're going to love! It has been well-cared for and is mechanically sound, showing only the typical minor cosmetic marks from careful daily use. It's a solid, high-quality performer that's prepared to serve its next owner faithfully for years to come!",
