    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is perfect for someone looking for a reliable mode of transportation without the price tag of a newer model. While the engine and transmission are solid and have been regularly serviced, the exterior shows noticeable signs of age, including some paint fading on the hood and minor dings from daily use. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some wear and staining consistent with its mileage. It\u2019s a dependable car that starts every time and handles well on the road, making it an excellent choice for a commuter or a first-time driver.",
      "price": 21000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep, mirror-like finish and no chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with high-quality materials that show zero signs of wear and still retain a new-car scent. Every mechanical component has been meticulously maintained, ensuring the car drives perfectly with no issues whatsoever. This is a collector-grade example that has been kept in a climate-controlled environment and is ready for its next owner to enjoy without any additional investment.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
